There's obviously been a lot of discussion about universal basic income, and welfare, and I barely know anything about it. But I can tell you how it makes me feel to know that someone else, my community, my country has my back and there is only so far I can fall. Runway, protection, and time give you the opportunity to take risks and innovate. In our world, money buys you all those things, but we should add additional paths towards safety outside of independent accumulation of wealth.

